criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  The participant is between the age of 18-26;

          -  University of Delaware student;

          -  Willing and able to commit to the 5-week study at specified time;

          -  Has a history of body dissatisfaction as indicated by high survey scores on body
             satisfaction and high scores on dietary restraint; and

          -  Are not currently being treated for an eating disorder.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Females who are currently diagnosed with and/or seeking treatment for an eating
             disorder.
